---
import { LINKS, SITE } from '../data/site'
---

<section
  id="inicio"
  class="relative pt-10 mt-28 w-full h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start text-white overflow-hidden"
  style="background-image: url('/images/ucm-bg-paramedic.jpeg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;"
>
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/60 via-black/20 to-black/60 backdrop-blur-[2px]"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="relative z-10 container-md flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left max-w-3xl"
  >
    <div
      class="mb-4 px-4 py-1 bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-md rounded-full text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide animate-fadeInUp"
      style="animation-delay:50ms"
    >
      Ejecutiva Oficial UCM • Atención rápida
    </div>
    <h1
      class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight drop-shadow-[0_4px_8px_rgba(0,0,0,0.6)] opacity-0 translate-y-4 animate-fadeInUp"
      style="letter-spacing:-1px; animation-delay:50ms"
    >
      Cotiza tu Plan UCM con Ejecutiva Oficial
    </h1>
    <p
      class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-xl opacity-0 translate-y-4 animate-fadeInUp"
      style="animation-delay:100ms; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-weight:500; line-height:1.6;"
    >
      Respuesta inmediata por WhatsApp. Orientación rápida y clara sobre tu plan UCM.
    </p>
    <div
      class="w-full mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 opacity-0 translate-y-4 animate-fadeInUp"
      style="animation-delay:150ms"
    >
      <a
        href={LINKS.wa()}
        target="_blank"
        data-cta="whatsapp"
        aria-label={`Contactar por WhatsApp a ${SITE.name}`}
        class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#25D366] hover:bg-[#1EBE5A] text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 text-lg rounded-xl shadow-xl shadow-black/20 transition-transform hover:scale-[1.03]"
      >
        Cotizar por WhatsApp
      </a>

      <a
        href={LINKS.call()}
        data-cta="llamar"
        aria-label={`Llamar a ${SITE.name}`}
        class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white text-[#1A2A42] font-semibold px-8 py-3 text-lg rounded-xl shadow-xl shadow-black/20 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-transform hover:scale-[1.03]"
      >
        Llamar ahora
      </a>
    </div>
    <p
      class="text-sm mt-3 opacity-0 translate-y-4 animate-fadeInUp"
      style="animation-delay:200ms; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)"
    >
      Respuesta rápida • Atención en {SITE.city} • Ejecutiva oficial UCM
    </p>
  </div>

  <style>
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
    .animate-fadeInUp {
      animation: fadeInUp 0.7s ease-out forwards;
    }
  </style>
</section>
